[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "お待たせしました！\n必要そうな素材を集めてきました！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "おお、レスナ殿に、皆様！\nお久しぶりでございまする！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "鬼門！　久しぶり！\nあれ、なんか結構人が集まってる？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "拙者、鏑矢様の計らいで休暇をいただいておりまする！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "リラ",
		"romanized_name": "Lila",
		"model_path_hash": "6420784340983749558",
		"text": "そんな折に、鬼門と再会できるとは。\nケイウン以来だな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "658330190563200680",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "あたしとレイニャはさっきまで無数島群域を巡ってて、\n帰ってきたところ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "レイニャ",
		"romanized_name": "Lenja",
		"model_path_hash": "5067796612903841500",
		"text": "調査団への報告が終わって、\n少し休んでいました",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "326916344881311074",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "なるほどねー……む？　むむむ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "どうしたの、アルビーナ？　そんなに唸って。\nもしかして、お腹痛い？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "違うわい！　いやなんかさ。\nみんな頭に耳が生えてるなーって",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "確かに……！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "……ねえ、みんなにも参加してもらおうよ！　優勝を\n狙うなら、可能性は少しでも高いほうがよくない？　",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "リラ",
		"romanized_name": "Lila",
		"model_path_hash": "6420784340983749558",
		"text": "いったい、なんの話だ……？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "658330190563200680",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "なるほど、武道会でございまするか。\n拙者、腕試しとまいりましょう！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "リラ",
		"romanized_name": "Lila",
		"model_path_hash": "6420784340983749558",
		"text": "悪くない。手ごわい相手と戦わないと\n腕がなまると思っていたところだ。力を貸すぞ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "658330190563200680",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "よく分かんないけど、やるやる！\nなんだか面白そうだし！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "レイニャ",
		"romanized_name": "Lenja",
		"model_path_hash": "5067796612903841500",
		"text": "レイニャ……ダメダメだけど、\n皆さんの役に立てるなら……頑張ります……！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "326916344881311074",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "よっしゃ！　これで戦力２倍だね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "じゃあ、改めて詳細を確認しましょう。\n会場となるのは、広大な砂漠です",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "そこに参加者が一斉に放り込まれて、最後まで倒れずに\n残った者が勝利、という単純明快な戦いです",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "武器や道具の持ち込みは自由なんだよね。\nアタシはもちろん、ハンマーを持っていくよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "最後まで倒れず残った者が勝利とのことだが……\n参加者同士で結託することは問題ないんだな？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "大丈夫そうですが……国王陛下の\n「生き様を見せろ」という言葉が気になります",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "知力や団結力もまた力っしょ！　……でもまぁ、\n全員並んで仲良く優勝ってわけにはいかないかと",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "リラ",
		"romanized_name": "Lila",
		"model_path_hash": "6420784340983749558",
		"text": "真剣勝負が求められているのだろう？\nならば、唯一の勝者は決めねばな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "658330190563200680",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "もし我々だけが残ったとしても、\n最後は恨みっこなし、ということでございまするね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "レイニャ",
		"romanized_name": "Lenja",
		"model_path_hash": "5067796612903841500",
		"text": "ひぇ。皆さんと、戦う……？\nやられたふりの練習をしておきます……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "326916344881311074",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "まぁ、誰かが勝てばそれでヨシ！\n目指せ、優勝ー！！！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "みんな",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おー！！！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "ケイウン南部の領主に仕えている忍者。\n「忍法」と呼ばれる様々な術を使う",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "リラ・ディザイアス",
		"romanized_name": "Lila Decyrus",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "流浪の戦士。オーレン族「白牙氏族」の生き残り。\nアンペルと共に各地を旅している",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "658330190563200680",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "リアス・アイトライゼ",
		"romanized_name": "Rias Eidreise",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "人懐っこい性格の元気な冒険者。\n謎の災害に見舞われた町「ハルフェン」出身",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "レイニャ",
		"romanized_name": "Lenja",
		"model_path_hash": "5067796612903841500",
		"text": "アラディス調査団所属、亜人種「ウェルクス」の少女。\n小心者だが、高い身体能力を活かした戦闘が得意",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "326916344881311074",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]